<h4>Step 3. <strong>Publish</strong></h4>
<p>Every time you hit the publish button we scan for new posts 
  and publish them on <a href="<%= @site_url %>">
  <%= if @site_url then @site_url.substr(7) else "your own url" %></a></p>
<div class="actions">
  <button class="publish full-width">Publish</button>
</div>
<div class="status"></div>
<div class="visit"><a href="<%= @site_url %>">
  <%= if @site_url then @site_url.substr(7) %></a> is ready</div>